{"tid":1265742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最新蕭析派定心丸：林鄭完成任期機會低，中央不會撕爛面皮整治香港","createTime":"2019-06-29T10:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T08:16:27.000Z","uid":30561,"like":7,"dislike":405,"uniUserReply":121,"replies":[{"pid":"ee80ec060f34dfcafc25c40605d90074935aa4fc","tid":1265742,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T10:33:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n- 林鄭能夠完成本屆任期機會渺茫<br />\n<br />\n- 香港獨特地位仍然重要，中央不會撕爛塊面來對待<br />\n<br />\n- 七一後中央收緊對香港控制機會不大，只要不犯重罪就無事</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=cftED6Tn60o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcftED6Tn60o&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmq7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=a6e47d63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=cftED6Tn60o</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係其他重要蕭析：<br />\n<br />\nJun 28, 2019<br />\n蕭若元估計G20將會提及香港，七一後不會大規模搜捕義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p8dt1Nm7pcA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp8dt1Nm7pcA&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmq7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=d0ba22c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p8dt1Nm7pcA</a><br />\n<br />\n Jun 25, 2019<br />\n十萬火急重要消息！ 三大銀行可能被制裁 香港關係法岌岌可危〈蕭若元：蕭氏新聞台〉<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IwmoARBHSKg?t=108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIwmoARBHSKg%3Ft%3D108&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmq7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=d2d97ea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IwmoARBHSKg?t=108</a><br />\n根據《2019年香港人權與民主法案》政策聲明（Statement of policy）第4條內容，「支持香港建立真正的民主選舉，自由和公平地提名和選舉香港行政長官，並在2020年前為香港立法會所有成員舉行公開和直接的民主選舉。」"},{"pid":"d3c4a4d59cd8f1d1eab8476557a9f89cfaa188b3","tid":1265742,"uid":43197,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"燒山"},{"pid":"51d0c108641e857722cdb50c66822ea4789aa1cd","tid":1265742,"uid":258646,"like":219,"dislike":0,"score":219,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-2